{"tid":1916961,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"連衛兵經常用嘅「標題」大家快啲入嚟睇吓啦","createTime":"2020-03-09T07:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T11:00:34.000Z","uid":216555,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"26dec5eddb0e357790f3acfccf88efef7bdf7827","tid":1916961,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"我屌哂你哋老母 係咪光復左香港 五大訴求達到左啦？<br />\n做咩成個熱門都係食玩膠同睇女post？<br />\n如果呢個post上唔到熱門 冇哂行動post 我正式宣布呢個運動真係玩完 連登已死<br />\n連我個淺藍老母都問啲暴徒係咪搞完事 外國戰線著哂火咁大粒核彈都冇人理既？￼<br />\n<br />\n應承我 唔可以當手足係condom？<br />\n我哋揸住佢個春袋 呢粒核彈會令到中共好驚 手足就嚟贏 千祈唔可以中五毛分化撚嘅計 推走熱門行動Post 唔係我哋就嚟輸<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可 煲底見！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d1Sd4r4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1Sd4r4.gif&h=66d0f8d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LDJXMFq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDJXMFq.gif&h=940bac12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連衛兵最撚鍾意調高黃絲標準<br />\n<br />\n分化港鐵前線職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近期仲話九巴公司係紅底 叫人擺搭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母行路啦仆街</span></span><br />\n分化泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞丁唔夠黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n煤氣公司係恆基紅底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n水務局係政府係港共政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母你班柒頭沖凍水涼啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢間鋪頭 唔夠黃 要擺買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲狗跑步仆街  都可以講足成晚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4204bcbeb5eee960dd1b27acaf816666f13c2007","tid":1916961,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"仲有一點<br />\n班連衛兵提高完標準 <br />\n你問下佢哋上咗神枱嘅人點計<br />\n例如 黃子華勾結東張西望 森美用華為上tvb<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連衛兵惡到直接叫你咪嘈"},{"pid":"e299284bd888c50d93bcf7551d77460776f5a769","tid":1916961,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:02:58.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"766fc760982399f2e58378f957cd6daeba292663","tid":1916961,"uid":216555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4204bcbeb5eee960dd1b27acaf816666f13c2007","tid":1916961,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"仲有一點<br />\n班連衛兵提高完標準 <br />\n你問下佢哋上咗神枱嘅人點計<br />\n例如 黃子華勾結東張西望 森美用華為上tvb<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連衛兵惡到直接叫你咪嘈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:03:30.000Z","msg":"周柏豪上微博叫人投票 post黑色相 咩顏色大家心照連衛兵都仲要屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e98b11e2d38a4def2c7e7fd1fc55ae102f836ed","tid":1916961,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4204bcbeb5eee960dd1b27acaf816666f13c2007","tid":1916961,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"仲有一點<br />\n班連衛兵提高完標準 <br />\n你問